emie (bis 1823). L. verfasste zahlreiche Schriften, u.a. \"El\u00e9ments raisonn\u00e9s d'alg\u00e8bre\" (1804), \"El\u00e9ments d'analyse g\u00e9om\u00e9trique et d'analyse alg\u00e9brique\" (1809) und mit Pierre Prevost vier Studien zur Wahrscheinlichkeitslehre (ver\u00f6ffentlicht in \"M\u00e9moires de l'Acad\u00e9mie des sciences de Berlin\" 1796-97)."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q123478", "itemLabel": "Simon Antoine Jean L'Huilier", "dhsid": "025661", "namefr": "Simon Antoine Jean L'Huillier", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simon_Antoine_Jean_L%27Huillier", "namede": "Simon L\u2019Huilier", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simon_L%E2%80%99Huilier", "nameit": "Simon Antoine Jean Lhuilier", "articleit": "https://it.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simon_Antoine_Jean_Lhuilier", "nameen": "Simon Antoine Jean L'Huilier", "articleen": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simon_Antoine_Jean_L%27Huilier", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "100189555"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q123478", "wikipedia_page_title": "Simon L\u2019Huilier", "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": "L", "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/de/articles/025661/2009-03-19"}